&lt;p&gt;This role is responsible for owning and growing a portfolio of Commercial accounts by driving expansion ARR and durable NRR outcomes. This role leads structured expansion and renewal strategies across moderate-complexity accounts, delivering predictable revenue growth through disciplined account planning, multi-product adoption, and value-based commercial execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and deliver expansion ARR quota and renewal performance within assigned Commercial accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute structured account plans focused on multi-product adoption and wallet-share growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead complex discovery and expansion conversations across multi-stakeholder buying groups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive disciplined renewal strategy, negotiation, and retention execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage larger deal sizes and moderate sales cycle complexity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate revenue forecasting and pipeline inspection discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with CX, Product, and Solutions to ensure alignment on expansion strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify commercial risk signals and proactively mitigate renewal exposure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure clean commercial handoffs where role transitions are required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other duties and responsibilities as required to support business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typical experience: 3-5 years in related role or experience.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actual experience may vary depending on role complexity, geography, and internal development opportunities or a comparable mix of training, education, and experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing Commercial account portfolios with ARR responsibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to drive expansion and renewal growth in multi-stakeholder environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong negotiation and commercial strategy capability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with structured sales methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;University degree preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing multi-product portfolios.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience navigating competitive displacement or pricing negotiations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting Commercial or mid-market segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
