&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As an experienced communications and strategy professional, this role will actively engage in client and sales discussions, leveraging expertise in content creation and writing to develop and implement effective content strategies. In addition, the role will enhance the diversity of product offerings by supporting multichannel solutions, and lead the coordination of internal and external resources to advance a solution-based selling strategy tailored to local client needs. The role also requires expanding and managing partnerships with external vendor resources to ensure quality and efficiency in service delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
