&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct consultation sessions with clients, develop and implement comprehensive, multi-channel content strategies for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce engaging, high-impact content to help clients achieve their business objectives, with a strong focus on high-quality press release writing and brand storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create analysis reports for clients with actionable content optimization suggestions and data-driven insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in client content planning meetings and client visits. Confidently present and explain content strategies and integrated communication plans to key stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay abreast of global communication trends, particularly within the US and European media environments, and provide regular market insights and content recommendations to clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage PR Newswire’s MultiVu-Channel solutions (including Paid media, Earned Media, OOH, and more) to integrate press release strategies with broader digital marketing and earned media efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design customized communication solution packages based on local client needs and company service offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage External Vendor Resources to evaluate and select high-quality external vendors, establishing long-term partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with sales, marketing team to promote sales campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
