&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;English &lt;/strong&gt;proficiency (primary language for communication within the organisation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Accounting or Finance, and/or 1–3 years of relevant accounting experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of US GAAP (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a global, decentralised environment (preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Microsoft Excel skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NetSuite experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
